# Devices Monitoring

**Devices Monitoring**

Devices list, configuration, devices detailed info, alarming and historical data etc are included in devices monitoring page.

![Alt text](data:image/gif;base64,)

**Devices List**  
Devices can be classified automatically according to the devices poisoning area, and the devices can be checked through devices name and area name.

**Configuration Screen**  
Devices monitoring screen after finishing configuration design can be indicated, the devices running status is clear and data input operation can be activated. Remote devices start-off, remote parameters setting can be realized under authority permission.

**Devices Detailed Information**  
Some devices detailed information is included in this area. Devices name, devices alarming statics, devices serial number, order number, devices installation status can be displayed. Those information is written during devices adding convenient for users management.

**Alarming and Historical Data**  
Devices current alarming, historical alarming, key parameters historical data can be checked.
